summary: Doors inside of the Hall of Attainment and Hall of Countenence.
descriptionHtml: This simple mod just adds doors to the Hall of Attainment and Hall of Countenance in College of Winterhold so everyone can have a bit more privacy. Only the rooms with beds get the doors, the enchanting room, alchemy room etc. remain without doors. No known bugs. If you don\'t use the Nexus Mod Manager, just extract the archive to your Skyrim/Data folder to install this.
author: Mutak94
